Interface ISmartMap<K,V>

All Known Subinterfaces:
ISmartSortedMap<K,V>
public interface ISmartMap<K,V>
extends java.util.Map<K,V>

Specifies the operations of SmartMaps. Smart Maps are compatible with the standard Map interface, but add some functionality to them. They are implemented as simple decorators (see Gang of Four).

Author:
